{"tid":574054,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特表示如果“All in”會買蘋果，但自己還是要用三星","createTime":"2018-02-27T05:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T04:25:15.000Z","uid":141060,"like":53,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8b7e5bc33eb31d4aad44978b8b15480d11d9d8","tid":574054,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"2月27日消息，&ldquo;股神&rdquo;巴菲特，在上週六發表2018年致股東信後，接受了CNBC的採訪，在被問到如果&ldquo;all in&rdquo;一隻股票會選擇哪一個時，巴菲特表示人們認為我們的持有倉位反映了伯克希爾的喜好順序（富國銀行是持倉最多），但如果看過去一年的新晉買入規模來看，蘋果是我們買入最多的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/130545_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F130545_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4318957b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▲CNBC採訪巴菲特，圖片來自9to5Mac<br />\n<br />\n他認為，蘋果的生態系統的穩健程度達到了&ldquo;無與倫比&rdquo;的水平，另外蘋果的產品用戶粘度非常大，&ldquo;至少在心理和精神層面，人們非常、非常、非常認定他們正使用的產品，蘋果就是這樣的公司。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n但是有趣的是現年88歲的巴菲特一直在使用一部三星手機，每當庫克向他推薦iPhone時他都沒有接受，它告訴庫克只要我還沒有買iPhone那就證明市場還遠遠沒有飽和。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特真係窮撚  水果機都買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4df8c27cfa6dfb738873418feb1706d25362c81","tid":574054,"uid":78304,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T05:09:31.000Z","msg":"傻撚左， 買三星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffd79e8364623799fe57da4616b8542a62c4ed7","tid":574054,"uid":37735,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T05:15:02.000Z","msg":"買三叔<br />\n係根據自己個邊際效應決定<br />\n<br />\n買蘋果股票<br />\n是根據一般人個邊際效應決定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f8a9ebc100fc2a780e757b20c3ace7e0585ea3","tid":574054,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fffd79e8364623799fe57da4616b8542a62c4ed7","tid":574054,"uid":37735,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T05:15:02.000Z","msg":"買三叔<br />\n係根據自己個邊際效應決定<br />\n<br />\n買蘋果股票<br />\n是根據一般人個邊際效應決定<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T05:16:56.000Z","msg":"死老野又幫三星賣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df9bc831410ae21c6672c45d1c33870985e6bc7","tid":574054,"uid":17103,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://alajadi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Can-you-guess-which-phone-does-he-uses.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Falajadi.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FCan-you-guess-which-phone-does-he-uses.jpg&h=8f878133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無錯, 佢用緊呢部, 快 D 買啦喂! 接合式老爺機, 比起三星而家 D SmartPhone 襟用好多</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可惜佢睇唔起三星 D Smartphone <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3dba03e69a9e19cb7685575fcc70dfab2789ec2","tid":574054,"uid":17103,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T06:55:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180112/1276907/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180112%2F1276907%2F&d=MhzRSUmMWK0hiWjdug5Y8f%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a2b755cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180112%2F1276907%2F&h=41720198\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180112/1276907/</a><br />\n唔知點解有 D Source 會無左 &quot;掀蓋式&quot;, 關三星 D SmartPhone 鳩事咩.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買左股神笑鳩你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180112/640_f01908407aaee1a511b2f76d9d6ed6b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180112%2F640_f01908407aaee1a511b2f76d9d6ed6b6.jpg&h=b891af59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n股票買蘋果手機用三星　這才是價值投資的Style<br />\n3823出版時間：2018/01/12 00:08  \t<br />\n<br />\n巴菲特股票投資選擇蘋果，實際使用的手機則買三星。翻攝CNBC<br />\n處女座的「股神」巴菲特（Warren Buffett）征戰股海以「價值型投資」策略聞名，日常生活則以節儉著稱，反映在手機投資採購上，巴菲特選股投資買生產iPhone的蘋果（Apple），實際使用則買與iPhone對打的三星（SAMSUNG）手機。<br />\n <br />\n若以粗淺的「價值型投資」原則分析，巴菲特看好蘋果（Apple）具備長線投資潛力，iPhone等產品利潤頗豐厚。至於實際手機產品採購，也許對巴菲特來說，蘋果、三星2大一線手機廠中，同級產品三星賺得比蘋果少，產品的售價可能是低估的，性價比相對較高。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">巴菲特周三接受美國財經媒體CNBC訪問時展示他的三星掀蓋式手機，他似乎不急著改用智慧手機。</span></span>巴菲特說，他自己是顯著還沒使用iPhone的例子，這顯示蘋果iPhone的市場尚未飽和。<br />\n <br />\n他開玩笑的表示：「當我真的買了，一切就結束了，（我是）最後一個買它的人。」可以肯定的是，巴菲特絕非唯一一個尚未使用iPhone的人。<br />\n <br />\nFactSet數據顯示，巴菲特持有1.34億股蘋果股票，這些股票價值約230億美元（約6808億元台幣）。巴菲特去年8月向CNBC表示，他2016年首次買進蘋果股票以來不曾拋售任何一股蘋果股票。（財經中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"1fb4df16fc623928c2b2741c680be3f75d8cb781","tid":574054,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:29:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">告訴庫克只要我還沒有買iPhone那就證明市場還遠遠沒有飽和<br />\n</span><br />\n有睿智嘅生意人，都可以比到三叔契弟搵到位入，真係欽敬，欽敬。"},{"pid":"32bf000ef4d1ac24e513e332047f1a9baaf61574","tid":574054,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:32:31.000Z","msg":"有錢到佢咁洗撚用電話咩，講一聲隔離個秘書乜都做晒啦"},{"pid":"418e95dad9e9323d0b592aeafd5831212f34e8ec","tid":574054,"uid":89514,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:39:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ce9d666abd31655f89fcd32e0b51fe41e554632","tid":574054,"uid":4895,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T